Fast Links App is the fastest and most convenient means to share links quickly from your browser window.

Add, Edit, Delete, Organize, Reorganize your links.

Need an affiliate link, payment link, or your calendar, all easily accessible from Fast Links App.

Fast Links App is the fastest way to share you links from your web-browser.

Fast Links App is a Google Chrome expansion as well as needs a Chromium browser in order to run.
